data.description: This Charming and Cozy Home has so much for You to Love. One Level 3BR/2BA Split Bedroom Floor Plan plus Future Expandable Up. Welcoming Entry Hall Leads to Great RM w/New Wide Plank Light Barn Wood Laminate Floors (including BR's), Gas Log Fireplace and Tall Ceiling. All Bedrooms have Coffered Tray Ceilings. Primary BR w/Ensuite, 2 Closets, Spacious Shower & Whirlpool Tub. Relaxing Covered Back Patio, Fenced in & Landscaped Yard. New Roof '22; New Hot Water Heater '20; New HVAC '18.
